description: Welcome to this spacious and beautifully designed 2-bed, 2-bath condo in vibrant South Boston. This home offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. The expansive living and dining area is perfect for entertaining, with an abundance of natural light flowing through large windows. The modern kitchen features sleek finishes, quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. Retreat to the king-sized primary suite, which is a true oasis with ample space, an en suite bath offering a glass enclosed rainfall shower, radiant floors, double vanity and an expansive walk-in closet with a California Closet system. Step outside to your own deeded patio space, perfect for enjoying the outdoors. Additional features include a second spacious bedroom, a full second bathroom, Sonos surround sound and hardwood floors throughout and garage parking. Enjoy easy access to the best of Southie’s exciting restaurants, parks, and beaches, and just a short distance from downtown Boston.
